data.title: Hailey Whitters Presale Information for Great Jones County Fair
data.meta_description: Here's everything you need to know to purchase tickets during Sunday's presale.
data.text:
Hailey Whitters is coming to the Great Jones County Fair in Monticello on Sunday, July 21. Since you're signed up for Concert/Event alerts on the 98.1 KHAK app, we're giving you the chance to buy your tickets before anyone else!

Beginning at 10 a.m. Sunday (February 11), you'll have access to an exclusive presale. Presale tickets will be available until 10 p.m. Sunday or until sold out. Tickets go on sale to the general public on Monday, February 12 at 10 a.m.

The code word is: 52338

Here's how to get your presale tickets:

Click HERE to go to E-tix.

Enter the code word: 52338

Select how many tickets you'd like to purchase. There is a limit of four tickets for this presale.

Buy your tickets and get ready to see Hailey Whitters at the 2024 Great Jones County Fair!

KHAK Welcomes Hailey Whitters

When: Sunday, July 21

Where: Great Jones County Fair in Monticello

Tickets: Tickets will be available until 10 p.m. Sunday night (February 11) or until they are sold out. The remainder of the tickets for the show will go on sale Monday, February 12 at 10 a.m.
